Babajide Sanwo-Olu, governor of Lagos, has been elected as the governorship candidate of the All Progressives Congress (APC) for the 2023 general election. The result was announced on Thursday during the primary which held at the Mobolaji Johnson arena, formerly known as Onikan stadium, on Lagos Island. Sanwo-Olu secured 1,170 votes out of a total of 1,198 accredited votes. More to followâ€¦